  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the script it was that all the blacks survive, and Jan said I tore the script book up, and I finished it the way I wanted it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the black people were executed in this movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there is one little boy who kind of looking at you before he gets shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's when the movie ends and gets stop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as long as I live, I will remember that picture and that ending.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said that would have been phony the other way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And naturally, he was never-- his pictures didn't bring in money, but he made statements.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- so I felt when I told you that in my bakery story I would bring in for a dramatic point of view and also to-- to make a statement that everybody would have been dead, it would give a much better understanding, a picture of that era.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was telling you a true story with a true ending that people survived, although I don't know what happened to the people later on in that building.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could have died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the building could have, but-- but in my mind, it would have been-- so that's why.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1944, probably November.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably November.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, besides the Germans, the Hungarian Arrow Cross, the air raids, there was a problem of what do you eat?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you drink?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to make a point and make a story somewhat shorter is that we ate everything what we could put our hands on.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
